pageContext.claim: “Now we've done 14 million tests. The second country is at 3 million and less than 3 million -- Germany, South Korea. And they've done a good job, but we're at 14 million tests, and the tests are the best of all.”
pageContext.analysis: Actually, Russia at the time was second with about 8 million tests. South Korea conducted about 800,000 tests.
